Response Text: To those new to the Arts and Culture sector: ASK QUESTIONS to the resources within the department.

Please do not throw away years of important and impactful work because a small sector of the community has the privilege of being the loudest and most present in the room. The arts commission has presented specific adjustments to the existing programs that should be implemented before starting over from scratch. That is how pilots work. Organizations that were historically underfunded due to systemic barriers have received transformational funding and have done amazing things. Talk directly to them and ask the questions around improvements and changes. 

AI is not going to paint the whole picture so please do not put all your faith into it just to meet a fabricated deadline.

